Atlas Copco unit to close Brazil plant . Swedish industrial engineering group Atlas Copco AB said on Thursday its unit Uniroc AB has decided to phase out its production unit in Sao Paulo , Brazil . The unit , that makes rock drilling tools , will be relocated to existing units in Sweden and Johannesburg , South Africa . " By relocating the production , Uniroc will get more rational manufacturing and substantial decrease of delivery times , " the company said in a statement . It said the aim was to phase out the Brazilian production unit which employs 84 staff by the end of the year . Uniroc is a division within Atlas Copco ' s construction and mining technique business area with its head office in Fagersta , Sweden . - - Stockholm newsroom + 46 - 8 - 700 1017 
